title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Sunset Skyway Bridge
description:
In this video we will fly over the Sunset Skyway Bridge.  The bridge consists of a pair of long beam bridges with a central cable-stayed bridge that spans Lower Tampa Bay to connect St. Petersburg, Florida to Terra Ceia. The current Sunshine Skyway opened in 1987 and is the second bridge of that name on the site.
